{"name":"Cleanse Impurity","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/aqueous-orb.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.sYdCIPxQ5yRYyZOx"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your power radiates from just a touch, causing impurities within the target to fade while bolstering your ally. Make a spell attack roll using the targeted poison or bleed effect&rsquo;s DC, with the following results.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your target gains a +4 status bonus to their next saving throw against that poison or bleed effect, and recovers [[/r 2d6]] Hit Points.<br><strong>Success</strong> Your target gains a +2 status bonus to their next saving throw against that poison or bleed effect, and recovers [[/r 1d6]] Hit Points.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your magic surges through the target uncontrollably, cleansing more than just your intended target. The target gains a +2 status bonus to their next save against the targeted effect, but they also take [[/r 1d8]] damage as their humours are forcibly purified.</p>\n<p>All dirt and grime are repelled from the target&rsquo;s body and clothes. This effect does not prevent the target from immediately becoming dirty once again, such as if they are standing in muddy water.</p>\n<p>If you use two actions to cast Cleanse Impurity, then the range is 30 feet, rather than touch.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2) </strong>Increase the healing given on a success and critical success by [[/r 1d6]] each.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["divine","hb_kannagi"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-01-07T17:53:12.021-05:00","version":{"schema":0.769,"foundry":"10.287","system":"4.2.6"}}},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":["divine"]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":"","areaType":""},"time":{"value":"1 or 2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"overlays":{"oruf5tel7pnjg98n":{"_id":"oruf5tel7pnjg98n","sort":1,"overlayType":"override"}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ChAfHXWjGQIj5GUP":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.287","createdTime":1673131992025,"modifiedTime":1676302500764,"lastModifiedBy":"ChAfHXWjGQIj5GUP"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"vuz0019fMwv4b5Yd"}
{"name":"Earthly Barrier","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/desperate-repair.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uNi6YLnclff42MjA"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Merging latent divine power with the spirits of the earth, you erect a magical barrier around your target. They gain 5 temporary Hit Points, which last for up to 1 minute. Additionally, your target gains resistance to piercing, slashing, or bludgeoning damage equal to half your level, rounded up (minimum 1). This resistance lasts until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> Increase the temporary Hit Points granted by 5.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"traits":{"value":["divine","hb_kannagi"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2023-01-07T17:53:24.987-05:00","version":{"schema":0.769,"foundry":"10.287","system":"4.2.6"}}},"level":{"value":1},"spellType":{"value":"utility"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":["divine"]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":"1 creature"},"range":{"value":"30 feet"},"area":{"value":"","areaType":""},"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"fixed","levels":{"2":{"damage":{"value":{}}}},"damage":{}}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ChAfHXWjGQIj5GUP":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.287","createdTime":1673132004990,"modifiedTime":1676302507206,"lastModifiedBy":"ChAfHXWjGQIj5GUP"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ylinF7Sml3CDSu2r"}
